snippet.title: Catizens — Early Access Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Imagine cuddly kitty cats, scratching posts, campfires, and... cabbages. Welcome to the cute kingdom of Catizens, a once peaceful land that is under attack. On August 17, 2022, prepare to build the purrfect pawesome settlements, train loyal furballs, and defend the realm from the evil rats and all manner of forest-dwelling creatures. 

Wishlist on Steam → https://store.steampowered.com/app/957660/Catizens/
